{"id":232964513,"title":"Legend","content":"國中才開始接觸籃球 接觸到NBA\n看你飛天遁地 各種後仰腳步美如畫 拿了2連霸\n那不講理的打法 看的真的讓我如癡如醉 \n後期阿基里斯腱斷裂 還堅持罰完自行走下場\n復出後的球隊雖然戰績一直都不佳\n但還是看你用盡全力 就是為了讓你的球迷看夠本\n\n大學2016/4/14 \n我翹課買了早午餐坐在房間看你的最後一場比賽\n原本就只是想看你開心打球而已\n沒想到還是一如往常的殺手風格 拿了60分\n2020應該是你要親自在現場看著自己的影片 \n聽著自己的名字 拿著自己的名人堂獎盃的年份\n上帝卻選擇先將你帶上去教他後仰跳投 低位腳步\n\n2020/1/27 我會一輩子記住這一天的\n我的籃球偶像&神&傳奇  8&24 R.I.P\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/268d2559-5ef6-46a2-a6fb-dbee4de875c4/full.jpeg\n                    \n                     I love you,Legend.","excerpt":"國中才開始接觸籃球 接觸到NBA，看你飛天遁地 各種後仰腳步美如畫 拿了2連霸，那不講理的打法 看的真的讓我如癡如醉，後期阿基里斯腱斷裂 還堅持罰完自行走下場，復出後的球隊雖然戰績一直都不佳，但還是看","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"863b960a-72a8-4479-80a2-b976275c002e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-27T01:57:06.692Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T09:50:12.864Z","commentCount":3,"likeCount":5,"tags":[],"topics":["NBA","籃球","心情","湖人","KobeBryant"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"籃球","forumAlias":"basketball","school":"明新科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":4},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/268d2559-5ef6-46a2-a6fb-dbee4de875c4/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"56262735-a2d0-48da-868a-5f1b38a3cb29","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/268d2559-5ef6-46a2-a6fb-dbee4de875c4/320.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/268d2559-5ef6-46a2-a6fb-dbee4de875c4/320.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/268d2559-5ef6-46a2-a6fb-dbee4de875c4/320.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-27T01:57:06.692Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T09:50:12.8